<html>
	<head>
		<title>BCM_ANYTEXT</title>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
	</head>
	<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
		<p><font color="#000000" size="4"><strong>BCM_REPLACESELECTION</strong></font></p>
		<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="3" width="100%">
			<tr>
				<td width="100%" bgcolor="#e6e6e6"><pre>BCM_REPLACESELECTION
	wParam = 0; 
	lParam = ( LPCTSTR )pszText;</pre>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		<p>Replaces the current text selection with the given text.</p>
		<UL>
			<li>
				Returns&nbsp;zero if there is no selection or the file is read-only. Returns 
				non-zero if the replacement is made.</li></UL>
		<DL>
			<DT><EM>pszText</EM></DT>
			<DD>
				A pointer to the 0-terminated text which is to replace the current selection.</DD></DL>
	</body>
</html>
